OL,3,CWill pension reforms 'unlock billions
OL,4,Cto drive growth'?
OL,6,FThe plan relates to defined benefit
OL,7,F(DB) pension schemes, also known as
OL,8,F"final salary" schemes as they often
OL,9,Fguarantee a specific income in
OL,10,Fretirement based on salary or length
OL,11,Fof service.
OL,13,FMost private sector companies have
OL,14,Fstopped offering DB schemes to their
OL,15,Fstaff because they are expensive - in
OL,16,Flarge part because people are living
OL,17,Flonger - but they are more common in
OL,18,Fthe public sector where the government
OL,19,Fbears the long-term financial risk.
