OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThere are 5,000 remaining DB schemes
OL,12,Fin the private sector.
OL,14,FThree quarters are currently in
OL,15,Fsurplus to the tune of #160 billion -
OL,16,Fthat is to say there is more than
OL,17,Fenough money set aside to make good on
OL,18,Fthe promises that have been made to
OL,19,Fcurrent and future retirees, based on
OL,20,Factuarial estimates of life expectancy.
