OL,3,CWill pension reforms 'unlock billions
OL,4,Cto drive growth'?
OL,6,FThe government sees these surpluses as
OL,7,F"trapped" money which, if released,
OL,8,Fcould flow into employee pay, business
OL,9,Finvestment or additional benefits for
OL,10,Fpension members.
OL,12,FTheoretically, the potential economic
OL,13,Fboost is huge. But there are buts.
OL,15,FSurplus money could be deployed for
OL,16,Fgrowth-rich investment. Less usefully,
OL,17,Fit could be used to help fund dividend
OL,18,Fpayments or share buybacks.
